column3: The Dibuk (Video)
column16: Years after their parents had made a pledge that they would marry, a young couple meet and fall in love. The father of the young man had long before perished and the young woman's father, forgetting his vow, keeps the two apart. column3: Bar Mitzvah (Video)
column16:
English subtitles/ 
Prosperous aristocratic widower on the eve of his son's bar mitvah announces his marriage to his young girlfriend, who plans to desert him as soon as she gets the money and property promised to her. The family as well as the widower still grieve over his former wife who was lost in a shipwreck on her way to America to visit her mother. On the day of the Bar Mitsvah, the lost wife, returns from America,  having survived the shipwreck, and having suffered from amnesia for the past ten years.
